title: Russia, America, and the Future of European Security
itunes:author: Professor Kristina Spohr, Dr Fiona Hill
description: Contributor(s): Professor Kristina Spohr, Dr Fiona Hill | A leading national security expert and best-selling author discusses Putin’s Russia, America’s future, and the implications of Russia’s invasion of Ukraine for the future of European security and democracy.
